cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.HC 

This paper focuses on training a humanoid robot to play a game using multiple modalities, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of deep reinforcement learning and multimodal perception and interaction also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of vision (cs.CV) and gestures (cs.HC) as part of the multimodal approach.
